    The Treasurer-Tax Collector's office welcomes you to information from
   their offices. This section will provide information on current County
     Investment-Pool Policy and Monthly Reports on the Investment Pool's
      status. We also provide information on Property Tax due dates and
     payment information, as well as information on the Tax Collector's
   Electronic Payment Option, including how to sign up and even the forms
   to download. Click Here to view the comprehensive list of forms offered
               by the Orange County Treasurer - Tax Collector.

                  Commenting on this page and on policies:

    The Treasurer - Tax Collector would like to hear your comments about
      what resources you'd like to see online and especially about your
                  thoughts on the Investment Pool Strategy.

     Our e-mail address is ttcinfo@treastax.co.orange.ca.us, or you may
                           contact us by mail at:

                  County of Orange Treasurer-Tax Collector
                           12 Civic Center Plaza
                            Santa Ana, CA 92701
